      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我注意到WaitServerHello之后有两条路径吗？还是说DeriveHPKE是必经之路？另外认证阶段WaitAuth是否需要处理失败分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WaitServerHello",
        "DeriveHPKE",
        "WaitAuth"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "DeriveHPKE是必须的，但WaitServerHello到DeriveHPKE的前提是收到valid ServerHello。WaitAuth确实要有两条分支：auth ok走向Established，auth fail则进入Error终止。另外Established之后还要支持Rekey状态，通过SessionKeyUpdate触发，然后回到Established。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WaitServerHello",
        "DeriveHPKE",
        "WaitAuth",
        "Established",
        "Error",
        "Rekey",
        "SessionKeyUpdate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下：Start从Infra_LoadBalancer进入，SendClientHello发出后等待服务器响应，收到有效ServerHello后派生HPKE密钥，发送认证并等待结果，成功则建立连接，失败报错。已建立连接后可通过SessionKeyUpdate进入Rekey，完成后回到Established。这个理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Start",
        "SendClientHello",
        "WaitServerHello",
        "DeriveHPKE",
