    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但注意Rekey和Established之间是双向循环的，Rekey完成后要回到Established。还有DeriveHPKE之后直接到SendAuth，中间没有其他状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
