      "utterance": "已绘制完成。从Infra_LoadBalancer指向Start，Start到SendClientHello，再到WaitServerHello。标注valid ServerHello条件后进入DeriveHPKE，接着SendAuth、WaitAuth。WaitAuth分出两条带条件的路径：auth ok到Established，auth fail到Error。Established通过SessionKeyUpdate触发Rekey，Rekey闭环回到Established。",
